<p>On my Ansible script, I'm using a loop to add lines to the apache2.conf file on the guest OS.  The lineinfile module inserts every line except the last one <code>&lt;/Directory&gt;</code>.  Why is Ansible skipping the final line?  Thanks.</p>  <pre><code>- name: test   lineinfile:     dest: /etc/apache2/apache2.conf     line: "{{ item.line }}"   with_items:      - { line: &lt;Directory /vagrant&gt; }     - { line: Options Indexes FollowSymLinks }     - { line: AllowOverride All }     - { line: Require all granted }     - { line: &lt;/Directory&gt; }   notify:     - restart apache2    </code></pre>